Interface IAnimatedArchitectureEventFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
AnimatedArchitectureEventFactorySpigot
public interface IAnimatedArchitectureEventFactory
Represents a class that can create IAnimatedArchitectureEvents.

    • createTogglePrepareEvent

      IStructureEventTogglePrepare createTogglePrepareEvent(StructureSnapshot snapshot, StructureActionCause cause, StructureActionType actionType, IPlayer responsible, double time, boolean skipAnimation, Cuboid newCuboid)
      Constructs a IStructureEventTogglePrepare.
      Parameters:
      snapshot - The snapshot of the structure.
      cause - What caused the action.
      actionType - The type of action.
      responsible - Who is responsible for this structure. Either the player who directly toggled it (via a command or the GUI), or the original creator when this data is not available.
      time - The number of seconds the structure will take to open. Note that there are other factors that affect the total time as well.
      skipAnimation - If true, the structure will skip the animation and open instantly.
      newCuboid - The Cuboid representing the area the structure will take up after the toggle.

    • createToggleStartEvent

      IStructureEventToggleStart createToggleStartEvent(AbstractStructure structure, StructureSnapshot structureSnapshot, StructureActionCause cause, StructureActionType actionType, IPlayer responsible, double time, boolean skipAnimation, Cuboid newCuboid)
      Constructs a IStructureEventToggleStart.
      Parameters:
      structure - The structure itself.
      structureSnapshot - A snapshot of the structure created at the time the toggle action was requested.
      cause - What caused the action.
      actionType - The type of action.
      responsible - Who is responsible for this structure. Either the player who directly toggled it (via a command or the GUI), or the original creator when this data is not available.
      time - The number of seconds the structure will take to open. Note that there are other factors that affect the total time as well.
      skipAnimation - If true, the structure will skip the animation and open instantly.
      newCuboid - The Cuboid representing the area the structure will take up after the toggle.

    • createToggleEndEvent

      IStructureEventToggleEnd createToggleEndEvent(AbstractStructure structure, StructureSnapshot snapshot, StructureActionCause cause, StructureActionType actionType, IPlayer responsible, double time, boolean skipAnimation)
      Constructs a IStructureEventToggleEnd.
      Parameters:
      structure - The structure.
      snapshot - A snapshot of the structure created when the structure was preparing to toggle.
      cause - What caused the action.
      actionType - The type of action.
      responsible - Who is responsible for this structure. Either the player who directly toggled it (via a command or the GUI), or the original creator when this data is not available.
      time - The number of seconds the structure will take to open. Note that there are other factors that affect the total time as well.
      skipAnimation - If true, the structure will skip the animation and open instantly.
